title: ssd Nand ic
message:
Which programmer is good for SSD nand upgrade in macbook models after 2018.
And is programmer required to change nand ic?

title: ssd Nand ic
message:
If you can pick the NAND from same model donor board, it will work directlly in the same position.
In case not exact donor available, then need P13 programmer.
[URL unfurl="true"]https://www.jcprogrammer.com/es/nand-programmer-p13.html[/URL]
Be aware, people reported that it can't do the black NAND chips, just the grey ones.
